snippet.title: Clash Of Evil - New Character Alert 2016
snippet.description: The biggest, deadliest, battle we've all anticipated is finally here! your favorite scary character is now available to play on mobile devices. Take on the best of the best in Clash Of Evil. Keep in the loops for more updates and characters.
